[
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"0464\" class=\"\">Eliphaz</st> the <st data-num=\"08489\" class=\"\">Temanite</st> <st data-num=\"06030 0559\">answered</st>: </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cDoes a <st data-num=\"02450\" class=\"\">wise man</st> <st data-num=\"06030\" class=\"\">answer</st> with <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">blustery</st> <st data-num=\"01847\" class=\"\">knowledge</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">or <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">fill</st> his <st data-num=\"0990\" class=\"\">belly</st><n id=\"2\" /> with the <st data-num=\"06921\" class=\"\">east wind</st>?<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Does he <st data-num=\"03198\" class=\"\">argue</st><n id=\"1\" /> with <st data-num=\"03808 05532\">useless</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">talk</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">with <st data-num=\"04405\" class=\"\">words</st> that <st data-num=\"03276\" class=\"\">have</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"03276\" class=\"\">value</st> in them?</p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">even</st> <st data-num=\"06565\" class=\"\">break off</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03374\" class=\"\">piety</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"01639\" class=\"\">hinder</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"07881\" class=\"\">meditation</st><n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> <st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">God</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sin</st> <st data-num=\"03588 0502\">inspires</st><n id=\"1\" /> your <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouth</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">choose</st> the <st data-num=\"03956\" class=\"\">language</st><n id=\"2\" /> of the <st data-num=\"06175\" class=\"\">crafty</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Your own <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouth</st> <st data-num=\"07561\" class=\"\">condemns</st><n id=\"1\" /> you, <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">your own <st data-num=\"08193\" class=\"\">lips</st> <st data-num=\"06030\" class=\"\">testify</st> against<n id=\"2\" /> you.</p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\">\u201cWere you the <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">first</st> <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">man</st> ever <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">born</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Were you <st data-num=\"02342\" class=\"\">brought forth</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> the <st data-num=\"01389\" class=\"\">hills</st>? </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Do you <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listen in</st> on <st data-num=\"0433\" class=\"\">God\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"05475\" class=\"\">secret council</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Do you <st data-num=\"01639\" class=\"\">limit</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"02451\" class=\"\">wisdom</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> yourself?</p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> do you <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> that we <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">What do you <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">understand</st> that <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">we</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">understand</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">The</st> <st data-num=\"07867\" class=\"\">gray-haired</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"03453\" class=\"\">aged</st> are on our side,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03524 03117\">men far older</st> than your <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Are <st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">God\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"08575\" class=\"\">consolations</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">too</st> <st data-num=\"04592\" class=\"\">trivial</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">for</st> you,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">or a <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">word</st> spoken<n id=\"3\" /> in <st data-num=\"0328\" class=\"\">gentleness</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">to</st> you?</p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st><n id=\"1\" /> has your <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st> <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">carried</st> you <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">away</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">why</st> do your <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st> <st data-num=\"07335\" class=\"\">flash</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">when</st> you <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">turn</st> your <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">rage</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">against</st> <st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">God</st><p class=\"poetry\">and allow such <st data-num=\"04405\" class=\"\">words</st> to <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">escape</st><n id=\"2\" /> from your <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouth</st>? </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> is <st data-num=\"0582\" class=\"\">man</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> he should <st data-num=\"02135\" class=\"\">be pure</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">or one <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">born</st> of <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">woman</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> he should <st data-num=\"06663\" class=\"\">be righteous</st>? </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">If</st> God<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0539\" class=\"\">places</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"0539\" class=\"\">trust</st> in his <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">holy ones</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">if even the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">heavens</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"02141\" class=\"\">are</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02141\" class=\"\">pure</st> in his <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st>, </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637 03588\">how much less</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st>, who is <st data-num=\"08581\" class=\"\">abominable</st> and <st data-num=\"0444\" class=\"\">corrupt</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">who <st data-num=\"08354\" class=\"\">drinks</st> in <st data-num=\"05766\" class=\"\">evil</st> like <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"02331\" class=\"\">explain</st> to you; <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listen</st> to me,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">what</st><n id=\"1\" /> I have <st data-num=\"02372\" class=\"\">seen</st>, I will <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">declare</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">what</st> <st data-num=\"02450\" class=\"\">wise men</st> <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">declare</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03582\" class=\"\">hiding</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">nothing</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">from the tradition of<n id=\"1\" /> their <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">to whom <st data-num=\"0905\" class=\"\">alone</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> was <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">given</st><p class=\"poetry\">when <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"02114\" class=\"\">foreigner</st> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">passed</st> <st data-num=\"08432\" class=\"\">among</st> them.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> his <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"07563 01931\">wicked man</st> <st data-num=\"02342\" class=\"\">suffers torment</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">throughout the <st data-num=\"04557\" class=\"\">number</st> of the <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> <p class=\"poetry\">that<n id=\"3\" /> are <st data-num=\"06845\" class=\"\">stored up</st> for the <st data-num=\"06184\" class=\"\">tyrant</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06343\" class=\"\">Terrifying</st> <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">sounds</st> fill<n id=\"1\" /> his <st data-num=\"0241\" class=\"\">ears</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">in a <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">time of peace</st> <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">marauders</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">attack</st> him.</p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He does <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0539\" class=\"\">expect</st><n id=\"1\" /> to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">escape</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> <st data-num=\"02822\" class=\"\">darkness</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> is <st data-num=\"06822\" class=\"\">marked</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">for</st> the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>;<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"05074\" class=\"\">wanders about</st>\u2014<st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st> for <st data-num=\"0344\" class=\"\">vultures</st><n id=\"1\" />\u2014 <p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">knows</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> of <st data-num=\"02822\" class=\"\">darkness</st> <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">is</st> at <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">Distress</st> and <st data-num=\"04691\" class=\"\">anguish</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01204\" class=\"\">terrify</st> him;<p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"08630\" class=\"\">prevail against</st> him <p class=\"poetry\">like a <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"06264\" class=\"\">ready</st> to launch an <st data-num=\"03593\" class=\"\">attack</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> he <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">stretches out</st> his <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">against</st> <st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">God</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"01396\" class=\"\">vaunts</st> himself<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">against</st> the <st data-num=\"07706\" class=\"\">Almighty</st>, </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06677\" class=\"\">defiantly</st> <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">charging</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">against</st> him<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">with a <st data-num=\"05672\" class=\"\">thick</st>, <st data-num=\"01354\" class=\"\">strong</st> <st data-num=\"04043\" class=\"\">shield</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Because</st> he <st data-num=\"03680\" class=\"\">covered</st> his <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">face</st> with <st data-num=\"02459\" class=\"\">fat</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06213 05921\">made</st><n id=\"2\" /> his <st data-num=\"03689\" class=\"\">hips</st> <st data-num=\"06371\" class=\"\">bulge with fat</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"07931\" class=\"\">lived in</st> <st data-num=\"03582\" class=\"\">ruined</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">towns</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and in <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">houses</st> where<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> one <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">lives</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">where</st> they <st data-num=\"06257\" class=\"\">are ready</st> to crumble into <st data-num=\"01530\" class=\"\">heaps</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06238\" class=\"\">grow rich</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and his <st data-num=\"02428\" class=\"\">wealth</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">endure</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">nor</st> will his <st data-num=\"04512\" class=\"\">possessions</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">spread</st> over the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05493 04480\">escape</st> the <st data-num=\"02822\" class=\"\">darkness</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"07957\" class=\"\">flame</st> will <st data-num=\"03001\" class=\"\">wither</st> his <st data-num=\"03127\" class=\"\">shoots</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and he will <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">depart</st> <p class=\"poetry\">by the <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">breath</st> of God\u2019s <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouth</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "30"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Let him <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0539\" class=\"\">trust</st> in <st data-num=\"07723\" class=\"\">what is worthless</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08582\" class=\"\">deceiving</st> himself;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"07723\" class=\"\">worthlessness</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> his <st data-num=\"08545\" class=\"\">reward</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "31"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">Before</st> his <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st><n id=\"1\" /> he will be <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">paid in full</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and his <st data-num=\"03712\" class=\"\">branches</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07488\" class=\"\">flourish</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "32"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Like a <st data-num=\"01612\" class=\"\">vine</st> he will <st data-num=\"02554\" class=\"\">let</st> his <st data-num=\"01154\">sour grapes</st> <st data-num=\"02554\" class=\"\">fall</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and like an <st data-num=\"02132\" class=\"\">olive tree</st> <p class=\"poetry\">he will <st data-num=\"07993\" class=\"\">shed</st> his <st data-num=\"05328\" class=\"\">blossoms</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "33"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <st data-num=\"05712\" class=\"\">company</st> of the <st data-num=\"02611\" class=\"\">godless</st> is <st data-num=\"01565\" class=\"\">barren</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">consumes</st> the <st data-num=\"0168\" class=\"\">tents</st> of those who accept <st data-num=\"07810\" class=\"\">bribes</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "34"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Job",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"02029\" class=\"\">conceive</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05999\" class=\"\">trouble</st> and <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">bring forth</st> <st data-num=\"0205\" class=\"\">evil</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">their <st data-num=\"0990\" class=\"\">belly</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">prepares</st> <st data-num=\"04820\" class=\"\">deception</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "35"
  }
]